Helo

253
00:19:57,770 --> 00:19:59,120
Kau nampak aku tak?

254
00:19:59,460 --> 00:20:01,520
P'Hill, kau boleh lepaskan aku

255
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:06,640
Terima kasih

256
00:20:07,730 --> 00:20:09,180
Sama-sama

257
00:20:09,230 --> 00:20:10,630
Kau okey sekarang, kan?

258
00:20:11,190 --> 00:20:13,350
Fah dan Arthit pun sangat risaukan kau

259
00:20:15,330 --> 00:20:16,470
Aku okey dah sekarang

260
00:20:17,840 --> 00:20:19,040
Nanti cerita lagi

261
00:20:19,130 --> 00:20:20,840
Patutnya aku ambil gambar sikit tadi

262
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:23,690
Tak sangka boleh nampak
sisi kau macam ni

263
00:20:25,840 --> 00:20:27,160
Aku gerak dulu

264
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:28,500
Jap, P'Jo, kau nak pergi ke?

265
00:20:28,590 --> 00:20:29,970
Ya

266
00:20:36,590 --> 00:20:38,810
Kenapa kau tak call aku
bila dah balik?

267
00:20:38,970 --> 00:20:41,210
Aku risau sangat tau

268
00:20:42,670 --> 00:20:44,880
Aku nak kejutkan kau

269
00:21:10,820 --> 00:21:12,580
Kau dekat sangatlah

270
00:21:15,550 --> 00:21:17,090
Aku rindu kau

271
00:21:17,800 --> 00:21:19,710
Aku nak rapat, nak tengok kau

272
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:34,030
Nak aku tolong dry rambut kau?

273
00:21:42,690 --> 00:21:44,210
Baik

274
00:21:44,900 --> 00:21:49,060
Jadi, kau kena pakai baju dulu

275
00:21:51,040 --> 00:21:51,680
Silakan

276
00:21:57,660 --> 00:21:59,300
P'Hill

277
00:22:19,650 --> 00:22:21,030
Dah siap

278
00:22:23,520 --> 00:22:24,810
Terima kasih

279
00:22:24,890 --> 00:22:26,750
Sama-sama

280
00:22:26,870 --> 00:22:29,410
Aku setiap hari dry rambut North

281
00:22:32,850 --> 00:22:34,930
Boleh aku cemburu dia ke?

282
00:22:36,030 --> 00:22:37,390
Tak boleh

283
00:22:45,230 --> 00:22:46,510
Kau buat apa tu?

284
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:48,260
Aku nak peluk kau

285
00:22:52,900 --> 00:22:54,900
Aku rindu kau

286
00:22:58,340 --> 00:22:59,920
Dah

287
00:23:03,070 --> 00:23:07,440
Tak payah stetoskop pun
aku boleh dengar degup jantung kau

288
00:23:07,940 --> 00:23:10,040
Kenapa boleh macam tu?

289
00:23:12,500 --> 00:23:14,170
Kau malu ke?

290
00:23:19,350 --> 00:23:20,870
Comelnya

291
00:23:28,640 --> 00:23:31,090
Lepaslah aku, P'Hill

292
00:23:32,320 --> 00:23:34,290
Boleh tunggu sepuluh minit lagi?

293
00:23:37,520 --> 00:23:39,240
Bagus macam ni

294
00:23:39,410 --> 00:23:41,730
Bila-bila masa aku nak jumpa kau pun boleh

295
00:23:48,210 --> 00:23:50,370
Kau okey tak?

296
00:23:51,490 --> 00:23:53,840
Aku rindu kau

297
00:23:55,220 --> 00:23:57,120
Aku bukan tanya pasal aku

298
00:23:57,430 --> 00:24:01,840
Maksud aku, apa jadi
lepas kau pergi tu?

299
00:24:05,750 --> 00:24:08,400
Ada masalah sikit

300
00:24:10,990 --> 00:24:13,880
Okay ke teruk?

301
00:24:15,080 --> 00:24:17,690
Semuanya berjalan lancar

302
00:24:18,420 --> 00:24:20,900
Nenek aku dah balik

303
00:24:21,490 --> 00:24:22,560
Balik

304
00:24:24,470 --> 00:24:27,270
- Dia dah sedar - Betul ke?

305
00:24:27,300 --> 00:24:28,130
Ya

306
00:24:28,180 --> 00:24:32,330
Aku gembira untuk kau,
baguslah macam tu

307
00:24:33,110 --> 00:24:34,060
Terima kasih

308
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:43,120
Masa aku sampai hospital

309
00:24:46,630 --> 00:24:48,880
- Mak - Hill

310
00:24:48,970 --> 00:24:52,820
- Apa jadi? - Nenek dah sedar

311
00:24:54,430 --> 00:24:57,010
- Betul ke? - Ya

312
00:25:04,500 --> 00:25:06,930
Doktor tengah buat pemeriksaan
dekat dia

313
00:25:07,000 --> 00:25:10,900
Atuk dan ayah ada kat dalam,
jom kita tengok dia

314
00:25:10,990 --> 00:25:13,840
Jom

315
00:25:15,910 --> 00:25:18,230
Aku sangat gembira

316
00:25:18,950 --> 00:25:21,310
Aku asyik sibuk di hospital

317
00:25:21,820 --> 00:25:24,540
- Tak sempat tengok telefon - Okey

318
00:25:25,630 --> 00:25:29,710
Dia sedar, memang terbaiklah

319
00:25:29,940 --> 00:25:31,850
Kan?

320
00:25:33,390 --> 00:25:36,870
Tapi kau nampak penat

321
00:25:37,310 --> 00:25:40,020
Sebab aku langsung tak tidur

322
00:25:40,680 --> 00:25:42,560
Lepas aku balik

323
00:25:42,670 --> 00:25:46,220
Aku terus call Johan
suruh dia bawa kau ke sini

324
00:25:47,280 --> 00:25:48,920
Baguslah

325
00:25:49,460 --> 00:25:51,460
P'Jo datang cari aku,
bukan kau

326
00:25:53,220 --> 00:25:54,760
Jujurnya

327
00:25:54,830 --> 00:25:57,110
Kau tak perlu pun jumpa aku cepat-cepat

328
00:25:57,170 --> 00:26:01,190
- Call aku saja, dah cukup - Tapi aku nak jumpa kau

329
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:03,500
Aku tak nak biar kau tunggu lama

330
00:26:04,470 --> 00:26:08,050
Okey, dah jumpa aku, pergi tidur lah

331
00:26:10,100 --> 00:26:12,530
Tapi banyak benda aku nak cerita

332
00:26:12,990 --> 00:26:15,040
- Boleh cerita lepas tidur - Tak boleh

333
00:26:15,100 --> 00:26:17,270
- Boleh - Tak boleh

334
00:26:18,610 --> 00:26:21,310
Okey, okey. Kau nak cakap apa?

335
00:26:21,700 --> 00:26:24,050
Ada soalan nak tanya?

336
00:26:29,990 --> 00:26:32,550
Boleh kau beritahu aku?

337
00:26:32,630 --> 00:26:36,480
Masa kau baru pindah sini
macam mana perasaan kau?

338
00:26:37,890 --> 00:26:39,920
Tak elok langsung

339
00:26:41,850 --> 00:26:45,350
Setiap hari aku merindui

340
00:26:45,840 --> 00:26:47,600
Dan rasa bersalah

341
00:26:47,700 --> 00:26:49,810
Juga kesedihan

342
00:26:51,970 --> 00:26:53,490
Setiap hari

343
00:26:53,710 --> 00:26:55,630
Aku asyik baca buku dalam bilik

344
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:57,360
Atuk nak aku

345
00:26:57,360 --> 00:26:59,390
Masuk fakulti perubatan
dapat markah paling tinggi

346
00:27:00,770 --> 00:27:02,900
Memang susah tau

347
00:27:05,390 --> 00:27:08,690
Kau langsung tak keluar ke?

348
00:27:08,810 --> 00:27:10,550
Ya

349
00:27:12,070 --> 00:27:13,970
Sebab apa jadi antara kita

350
00:27:14,040 --> 00:27:17,920
Atuk kunci aku dalam rumah
sampai aku masuk universiti

351
00:27:18,970 --> 00:27:21,410
Aku jarang jumpa sesiapa

352
00:27:24,190 --> 00:27:26,270
Patutlah

353
00:27:26,390 --> 00:27:29,390
Kau hilang dari hidup aku

354
00:27:30,250 --> 00:27:34,030
- Maaf - Tak apa, betul, tak apa

355
00:27:34,210 --> 00:27:36,220
Tak perlu minta maaf

356
00:27:36,950 --> 00:27:39,110
Tapi aku betul-betul fikir

357
00:27:39,310 --> 00:27:43,310
Kau tinggalkan aku

358
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:48,070
Lepas aku diterima masuk
fakulti perubatan, aku terus nak cari kau

359
00:27:48,490 --> 00:27:50,500
Tapi call tak masuk pula

360
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:53,370
Kenapa tukar nombor?

361
00:27:55,030 --> 00:27:59,140
Oh, sebab aku gaduh dengan keluarga juga

362
00:28:00,830 --> 00:28:02,910
Teruk ke?

363
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:07,260
Ya, kira teruk juga

364
00:28:08,490 --> 00:28:10,550
Sebenarnya

365
00:28:11,380 --> 00:28:15,220
Hari ayah aku datang rumah kau cari aku tu

366
00:28:15,420 --> 00:28:18,920
Kami bergaduh besar

367
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:24,130
Lepas tu setiap hari aku gaduh
dengan dia

368
00:28:24,690 --> 00:28:28,660
Jadi aku putuskan nak keluar dari rumah

369
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:31,600
Aku tukar nombor juga

370
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:37,010
Tapi sebenarnya aku duduk
dekat rumah saudara

371
00:28:37,270 --> 00:28:39,620
Aku rasa ayah aku mesti tahu

372
00:28:40,320 --> 00:28:42,840
Mak aku jarang-jarang call aku

373
00:28:43,090 --> 00:28:44,480
Lepas aku diterima belajar di U ni

374
00:28:44,840 --> 00:28:46,800
Aku terus pindah ke sini

375
00:28:48,430 --> 00:28:50,980
Sejak hari tu

376
00:28:51,590 --> 00:28:55,930
Aku tak balik rumah langsung

377
00:28:59,770 --> 00:29:03,190
Oh ya, P'Hill, aku dah cakap
dengan Christ

378
00:29:03,460 --> 00:29:06,160
Dia kata ayah aku
dah tak marahkan aku

379
00:29:08,210 --> 00:29:10,260
Baguslah

380
00:29:11,510 --> 00:29:15,870
Maknanya semua dah jelas,
takda salah faham dah

381
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:18,770
Ya

382
00:29:19,440 --> 00:29:22,150
Boleh aku cuba lagi?

383
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:28,340
Sepuluh minit dah habis,
lepaskan aku

384
00:29:28,490 --> 00:29:30,480
Tolong tambah masa sikit lagi

385
00:29:30,600 --> 00:29:33,240
- Boleh tak? - Masa kau dah tamat

386
00:29:33,920 --> 00:29:35,840
Jangan rapat sangat dah

387
00:29:58,230 --> 00:29:59,920
Apa yang kau sedang buat?

388
00:30:00,300 --> 00:30:02,290
Mari duduk sini.

389
00:30:05,540 --> 00:30:07,470
Aku dah balas.

390
00:30:08,020 --> 00:30:11,800
Baru nak balas? Nanti aku block kau!

391
00:30:12,190 --> 00:30:15,750
- Aku ingat kau nak aku balas. - Sebelum ini ya.

392
00:30:15,960 --> 00:30:17,670
Sekarang dah tak lagi.

393
00:30:18,420 --> 00:30:19,750
Dulu kau risaukan aku.

394
00:30:19,950 --> 00:30:22,460
Sekarang dah tak risau?

395
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:28,310
Betul-betul tak risau ke?

396
00:30:30,290 --> 00:30:31,720
Kau hantar banyak mesej.

397
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:35,040
Katanya nak cekik aku supaya aku cerita semua.

398
00:30:36,110 --> 00:30:37,940
Jadi macam mana?

399
00:30:39,530 --> 00:30:42,180
Ada apa-apa lagi nak cakap?

400
00:30:42,260 --> 00:30:44,110
Tapi kau tak cekik pun.

401
00:30:44,190 --> 00:30:46,160
Kalau macam tu aku tak nak cerita.

402
00:30:51,270 --> 00:30:53,350
Marilah.

403
00:30:55,090 --> 00:30:56,450
Aku main-main je.

404
00:30:56,510 --> 00:30:58,340
Lepaskan aku.

405
00:30:58,690 --> 00:31:01,610
Kau masih nak aku belanja pencuci mulut?

406
00:31:02,570 --> 00:31:03,720
Kalau kau tak lepas lagi

407
00:31:03,720 --> 00:31:06,550
Aku suruh kau belanja sampai poket kosong.

408
00:31:07,540 --> 00:31:10,430
Rasanya sepuluh tahun lagi pun aku masih belanja kau.

409
00:31:10,590 --> 00:31:13,030
Kau sanggup temankan aku sepuluh tahun lagi tak?

410
00:31:13,650 --> 00:31:17,510
Jangan cakap lagi. Lepaskan aku.

411
00:31:18,550 --> 00:31:20,400
Suka cakap yang bukan-bukan.

412
00:31:20,730 --> 00:31:22,150
Ter

413
00:31:23,390 --> 00:31:24,790
Apa?

414
00:31:26,070 --> 00:31:26,960
Aku cintakan kau.

415
00:31:32,270 --> 00:31:34,400
Aku pun cinta kau.

416
00:31:40,210 --> 00:31:44,340
Rasa macam mimpi kau sentiasa di sisi.

417
00:31:48,320 --> 00:31:50,110
Dulu aku fikir

418
00:31:50,280 --> 00:31:54,660
Kalau suatu hari kau ada di samping aku

419
00:31:56,080 --> 00:31:58,550
Atau kalau dapat jumpa kau lagi

420
00:31:59,250 --> 00:32:01,390
Walau hanya sekilas

421
00:32:01,720 --> 00:32:03,790
Aku sanggup buat apa saja untuk kau.

422
00:32:07,610 --> 00:32:09,320
Berilah aku peluang jaga kau lagi sekali.

423
00:32:19,390 --> 00:32:21,570
Sudi jadi teman lelaki aku?

424
00:32:28,450 --> 00:32:30,390
Sudi.

425
00:33:30,820 --> 00:33:34,360
Satu malam tak balas langsung.

426
00:33:34,450 --> 00:33:36,340
Tinggalkan aku sorang-sorang di sini.

427
00:33:36,790 --> 00:33:38,420
Macam mana?

428
00:33:38,820 --> 00:33:40,930
Korang dah bercinta ke belum?

429
00:33:47,280 --> 00:33:50,270
Nampak gaya macam dah.

430
00:33:50,350 --> 00:33:53,270
Korang dah buat ‘tu’, betul tak?

431
00:33:53,350 --> 00:33:55,640
Apa benda ni?

432
00:33:58,340 --> 00:33:59,660
Jadi macam mana?

433
00:33:59,710 --> 00:34:02,630
Dah sedia nak umum ke?

434
00:34:02,770 --> 00:34:04,410
Umum apa, North?

435
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:06,310
Perkara kau dengan P'Hill lah.

436
00:34:06,520 --> 00:34:10,600
Percayalah, nanti satu kampus tahu.

437
00:34:12,740 --> 00:34:15,450
Jangan cakap fasal aku, cerita hal penting.

438
00:34:15,730 --> 00:34:19,790
Aku baru jumpa tuan rumah, dia minta sewa.

439
00:34:21,070 --> 00:34:22,440
Asyik-asyik aunty tu.

440
00:34:22,520 --> 00:34:23,950
Jumpa je minta duit.

441
00:34:23,950 --> 00:34:25,120
Lambat sehari pun tak boleh.

442
00:34:26,890 --> 00:34:29,630
Tapi kau tak boleh tangguh setiap bulan.

443
00:34:30,640 --> 00:34:32,830
Aku bukannya tak nak bayar langsung.

444
00:34:33,910 --> 00:34:34,920
Sekarang je takde duit.

445
00:34:36,420 --> 00:34:38,260
Cuba tengok kau habiskan duit kat mana.

446
00:34:38,340 --> 00:34:41,350
Komputer, game, rak penuh model.

447
00:34:41,390 --> 00:34:43,690
Kalau jual semua ni, mesti kaya.

448
00:34:43,790 --> 00:34:45,560
Aku rasa semua ni cantik.

449
00:34:45,890 --> 00:34:49,540
Jangan pura-pura tak dengar. Habis, hal kau camne?

450
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:51,850
Apa aku nak buat?

451
00:34:52,200 --> 00:34:54,720
Masih nak pura-pura? Aku tanya pasal kau dan P'Johan.

452
00:34:54,770 --> 00:34:56,350
Korang dah bersama ke belum?

453
00:34:56,400 --> 00:35:00,460
P'Jo tanya fasal kau semalam, caring betul.

454
00:35:03,300 --> 00:35:05,050
Aduh, ngantuklah.

455
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:06,820
- Kenapa tiba-tiba ngantuk? - Nak tidur dah.

456
00:35:06,910 --> 00:35:08,480
Nak pergi mana? Sekarang tak boleh tidur!

457
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:10,070
Hari ni Sabtu, kau kena kerja di kedai P'Thun.

458
00:35:10,130 --> 00:35:12,790
Aku berjaga malam tadi.

459
00:35:12,870 --> 00:35:15,700
Biar aku tidur kejap, nap sekejap je.

460
00:35:15,810 --> 00:35:18,270
North, kau ni bagi alasan je.

461
00:35:18,420 --> 00:35:20,430
Jawab dulu.

462
00:35:21,390 --> 00:35:24,670
Aku tahu korang dah bersama, jangan pura-pura.

463
00:35:25,200 --> 00:35:27,180
Jawab dulu!

464
00:35:32,230 --> 00:35:34,890
Kek dan kopi kau.

465
00:35:35,070 --> 00:35:36,950
Hati-hati.

466
00:35:38,530 --> 00:35:40,600
Selamat menikmati.

467
00:35:48,700 --> 00:35:50,550
Masih rasa tertekan ke?

468
00:35:50,850 --> 00:35:53,110
Kalau kau kat tempat aku pun tekan jugak.

469
00:35:54,650 --> 00:35:56,750
Korang berdua kenapa?

470
00:35:57,340 --> 00:35:59,440
Itu...

471
00:36:01,140 --> 00:36:02,180
P'Thun

472
00:36:02,270 --> 00:36:03,940
Apa?

473
00:36:03,990 --> 00:36:08,950
Boleh aku pinjam dalam dua tiga puluh ribu baht?

474
00:36:09,130 --> 00:36:11,020
Hah?

475
00:36:12,830 --> 00:36:15,150
- Dua tiga puluh ribu? - Ya.

476
00:36:16,020 --> 00:36:18,830
Siapa nak bagi kau banyak tu?

477
00:36:19,960 --> 00:36:21,310
Tapi...

478
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:23,330
Kenapa kau perlukan duit banyak sangat?

479
00:36:24,030 --> 00:36:26,370
Nak bayar yuran dengan sewa asrama.

480
00:36:26,670 --> 00:36:28,280
Aku lupa nak bayar.

481
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:29,510
Lupa?

482
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:31,550
Duit tu dah beli komputer.

483
00:36:31,550 --> 00:36:34,000
- Apa? Beli komputer? - Ya.

484
00:36:34,550 --> 00:36:35,680
Padan muka.

485
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:38,410
Duit habis beli game komputer.

486
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:40,510
Tapi tak ada duit nak sewa tidur.

487
00:36:40,590 --> 00:36:43,350
Kalau aunty potong air elektrik, aku lenyek kau.

488
00:36:43,370 --> 00:36:44,840
Kenapa kau tak ingatkan aku?

489
00:36:44,840 --> 00:36:47,920
Aku dah cakap suruh minta tolong P'Johan, tapi kau degil.

490
00:36:47,980 --> 00:36:49,090
Tak nak.

491
00:36:49,140 --> 00:36:51,030
Aku tak nak sembang duit dengan P'Jo.

492
00:36:51,240 --> 00:36:53,830
- Tak mungkin. - Aku dah nak gila ni.

493
00:36:54,430 --> 00:36:56,410
Er... P'Thun, kau pun...

494
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:58,830
Bila boleh dapat gaji?

495
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,180
Gaji kau...

496
00:37:00,300 --> 00:37:02,960
Ah, memang aku nak cakap fasal ni.

497
00:37:03,570 --> 00:37:05,470
Ada orang nak beli kafe aku.

498
00:37:05,700 --> 00:37:07,490
Nak beli kafe ni?

499
00:37:07,940 --> 00:37:09,990
